@startuml
autonumber
actor User
participant "Face Detection Module" as FaceDetectionModule
participant "Hand Movement Detection Module" as HandMovementDetectionModule
participant "Gesture Recognition Module" as GestureRecognitionModule
participant "Face Recognition Module" as FaceRecognitionModule
participant "Hand Tracking Module" as HandTrackingModule
participant "Single-Hand Interaction Module" as SingleHandInteractionModule
participant "Customizable Gesture Module" as CustomizableGestureModule
FaceDetectionModule -> FaceRecognitionModule : Send face detection result
HandMovementDetectionModule -> HandTrackingModule : Send hand movement detection result
HandMovementDetectionModule ->> GestureRecognitionModule : Trigger gesture recognition
GestureRecognitionModule ->> SingleHandInteractionModule : Trigger single-hand interaction
GestureRecognitionModule ->> CustomizableGestureModule : Trigger gesture customization
HandTrackingModule -> SingleHandInteractionModule : Send hand tracking result
CustomizableGestureModule ->> SingleHandInteractionModule : Trigger single-hand interaction with customized gesture
@enduml